body:
I swear people will literally lie to themselves just because they dont like something. All of the other ultimate skins are NOT perfect

&quot;Oh well Lux has 10 different forms&quot;
- Well, yes but can only pick 2 per game and you have to charge up for it. And if you&#039;re behind,  have fun feeling worse with that base skin at 20 minutes.

&quot;Udyr has 4 forms you can switch through while fighting&quot;
-Weeeeeellll Udyr&#039;s ultimate skin is also his VGU lmao. 

&quot;Sona has music tied to hers&quot;
- Honestly at this point, who really listens to them -__-

- And Ezreal&#039;s ultimate is still showing its age even after the updates.

I know you may not like the fact that MF has so many fucking skins but dont act like the other skins are the pinnacle standard.
